<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Cmsis-Dap on Documentación UNIT</title><link>https://cesarbautista10.github.io/unit_blog_devlab/tags/cmsis-dap/</link><description>Recent content in Cmsis-Dap on Documentación UNIT</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>es</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 15:10:00 -0500</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://cesarbautista10.github.io/unit_blog_devlab/tags/cmsis-dap/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>CH552 Multi-Protocol - Modo CMSIS-DAP</title><link>https://cesarbautista10.github.io/unit_blog_devlab/avances/ch552-cmsis-dap-mode/</link><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 15:10:00 -0500</pubDate><guid>https://cesarbautista10.github.io/unit_blog_devlab/avances/ch552-cmsis-dap-mode/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;El &lt;strong&gt;CH552 Multi-Protocol&lt;/strong&gt; en modo CMSIS-DAP permite programar y depurar microcontroladores ARM Cortex-M usando el estándar de ARM.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="flashear-firmware-cmsis-dap"&gt;Flashear firmware CMSIS-DAP&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Descargar firmware&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;wget https://github.com/UNIT-Electronics/CH552-CMSIS-DAP/releases/latest/ch552_cmsis_dap.bin
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Flashear con WCHISPTool&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;wchisptool -f ch552_cmsis_dap.bin
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="conexiones-swd"&gt;Conexiones SWD&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;CH552 CMSIS-DAP Target ARM
════════════════ ═══════════
SWDIO ────→ SWDIO
SWDCLK ────→ SWDCLK
GND ────→ GND
3.3V ────→ VDD
RESET (opt) ────→ RESET
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h2 id="programar-con-pyocd"&gt;Programar con PyOCD&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Instalar PyOCD&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pip install pyocd
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Listar targets&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pyocd list
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Flashear firmware&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pyocd flash -t stm32f103 firmware.hex
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Para PY32F003&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pyocd pack install puya
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pyocd flash -t py32f003 firmware.hex
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="depurar-con-gdb"&gt;Depurar con GDB&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Terminal 1: Iniciar servidor GDB&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pyocd gdbserver -t stm32f103
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Terminal 2: Conectar GDB&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;arm-none-eabi-gdb firmware.elf
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;gdb&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; target remote :3333
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;gdb&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; load
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;gdb&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; break main
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;gdb&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;continue&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="arduino-ide-con-py32f003"&gt;Arduino IDE con PY32F003&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="1-instalar-soporte-py32"&gt;1. Instalar soporte PY32&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;Archivo → Preferencias → URLs Adicionales:
https://github.com/py32duino/platform-py32f0.git
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h3 id="2-configurar-programador"&gt;2. Configurar programador&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;Herramientas → Placa: PY32F003
Herramientas → Programador: CMSIS-DAP
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h3 id="3-cargar-sketch"&gt;3. Cargar sketch&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setup&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; pinMode(PA0, OUTPUT);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;loop&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; digitalWrite(PA0, HIGH);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; delay(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1000&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; digitalWrite(PA0, LOW);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; delay(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1000&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Presiona &lt;strong&gt;Ctrl+U&lt;/strong&gt; para cargar.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Programación PY32F003 con Arduino IDE</title><link>https://cesarbautista10.github.io/unit_blog_devlab/avances/py32f003-programming/</link><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 15:00:00 -0500</pubDate><guid>https://cesarbautista10.github.io/unit_blog_devlab/avances/py32f003-programming/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;El &lt;strong&gt;PY32F003&lt;/strong&gt; es un microcontrolador ARM Cortex-M0+ de Puya Semiconductor, ultra económico y compatible con Arduino IDE.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="características-py32f003l24d6tr"&gt;Características PY32F003L24D6TR&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🧠 &lt;strong&gt;CPU&lt;/strong&gt;: ARM Cortex-M0+ @ 24MHz&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;💾 &lt;strong&gt;Flash&lt;/strong&gt;: 20KB&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🧮 &lt;strong&gt;RAM&lt;/strong&gt;: 3KB&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;📌 &lt;strong&gt;GPIO&lt;/strong&gt;: 13 pines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🔌 &lt;strong&gt;Periféricos&lt;/strong&gt;: UART, I2C, SPI, ADC (12-bit)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;💰 &lt;strong&gt;Precio&lt;/strong&gt;: ~$0.10 USD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="instalación-arduino-ide"&gt;Instalación Arduino IDE&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Abre Arduino IDE&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ve a &lt;strong&gt;Archivo → Preferencias&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Agrega esta URL en &amp;ldquo;Gestor de URLs Adicionales&amp;rdquo;:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;https://github.com/py32duino/platform-py32f0.git
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ve a &lt;strong&gt;Herramientas → Placa → Gestor de placas&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Busca &amp;ldquo;PY32&amp;rdquo; e instala el paquete&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id="conexiones-ch552--py32f003"&gt;Conexiones CH552 → PY32F003&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;CH552 (CMSIS-DAP) PY32F003
═════════════════ ════════
SWDIO ────→ SWDIO (PA13)
SWDCLK ────→ SWDCLK (PA14)
GND ────→ GND
3.3V ────→ VDD
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;h2 id="ejemplo-blink-arduino"&gt;Ejemplo Blink (Arduino)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// PY32F003 Blink LED
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#define LED_PIN PA0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setup&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; pinMode(LED_PIN, OUTPUT);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;loop&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; digitalWrite(LED_PIN, HIGH);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; delay(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1000&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; digitalWrite(LED_PIN, LOW);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; delay(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1000&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="ejemplo-serial"&gt;Ejemplo Serial&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setup&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; Serial.begin(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;115200&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;loop&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; Serial.println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hola desde PY32F003!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; delay(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1000&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="ejemplo-adc"&gt;Ejemplo ADC&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#define ADC_PIN PA4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setup&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; Serial.begin(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;115200&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; pinMode(ADC_PIN, INPUT_ANALOG);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;loop&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; adcValue &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; analogRead(ADC_PIN);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;float&lt;/span&gt; voltage &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; (adcValue &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4095.0&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3.3&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; Serial.print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;ADC: &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; Serial.print(adcValue);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; Serial.print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34; | Voltaje: &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; Serial.print(voltage);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; Serial.println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;V&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; delay(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;500&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="configurar-programador"&gt;Configurar programador&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;En Arduino IDE:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>PyOCD - Depuración ARM Cortex-M</title><link>https://cesarbautista10.github.io/unit_blog_devlab/avances/pyocd-debugging/</link><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 14:45:00 -0500</pubDate><guid>https://cesarbautista10.github.io/unit_blog_devlab/avances/pyocd-debugging/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;PyOCD es una herramienta de línea de comandos y librería Python para depurar y programar microcontroladores ARM Cortex-M usando sondas CMSIS-DAP/DAPLink.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="instalación"&gt;Instalación&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Instalar PyOCD&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pip install pyocd
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Verificar instalación&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pyocd --version
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Listar dispositivos conectados&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pyocd list
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="instalar-packs-de-soporte"&gt;Instalar packs de soporte&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Para microcontroladores específicos:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Buscar pack&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pyocd pack find stm32
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Instalar pack&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pyocd pack install stm32f4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Para PY32F003&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pyocd pack install puya
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="flashear-firmware"&gt;Flashear firmware&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Flashear archivo .hex&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pyocd flash -t stm32f103 firmware.hex
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Flashear archivo .bin (especificar dirección)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pyocd flash -t stm32f103 --base-address 0x08000000 firmware.bin
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Auto-detectar target&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pyocd flash firmware.hex
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="depuración-con-gdb"&gt;Depuración con GDB&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Iniciar servidor GDB&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pyocd gdbserver -t stm32f103
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# En otra terminal, conectar GDB&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;arm-none-eabi-gdb firmware.elf
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;gdb&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; target remote :3333
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;gdb&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; load
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;gdb&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;continue&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="integración-con-vs-code"&gt;Integración con VS Code&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Archivo &lt;code&gt;.vscode/launch.json&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>